<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>152</hymn_number>
<author>mnạl smyr, mnạl smyr</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (yạ knysẗ qwmy wsbḥy .. ʿnk hmwmk ạ̹ṭrḥy
 llmjrwḥyn dmʿ ạ̹msḥy .. ʿnd yswʿ mlk ạlmlwk)2
 ạlqrạr- (mjdh ʿlyky yury̱)2
 wạ̹n gẖṭy̱ ạlạ̉rḍ ẓlạm .. mjdh ʿlyky yury̱
 2- (yạ knysẗ qwmy wdwry .. ʿly̱ ạlkẖrạf wnwry
 ạlmjd jạy ạ̹tḥḍry .. lmjyʾ yswʿ mlk ạlmlwk)2
 3- (ạ̉bwạb jḥym .. msẖ hạtqwy ʿlyky
 dh ạlrb ḥy .. sạkn fy wsṭyky
 wswr mn nạr .. mjdh mn ḥwạlyky
 qwmy ạ̹stnyry .. hw hạyfrḥ byky)2
 4- (yạ knysẗ qwmy wạnhḍy .. dh ạ̹lhk ḥy wạ̉bdy
 wmʿạh ạ̉frạḥk tbtdy .. hw yswʿ mlk ạlmlwk)2</lyrics>
<title>yạ knysẗ qwmy wsbḥy</title>
</song>